sentences.english: I repeated them until I could recite seventy stories without dropping a word.

sentences.english: Seventy-five years after Mrs. Graham's cat fell into the freezer.
sentences.chinese: 在格雷厄姆太太的貓掉進冰櫃七十五年之後。

sentences.english: What has Tyre changed seventy years after her judgement?

sentences.english: In seventy-seven years she has never said no.
sentences.chinese: 七十七年來她從未拒絕過別人。

sentences.english: I have arrived at seven billion myself, theoretically.
sentences.chinese: 在理論上，我自己得出的數字爲七十億。

sentences.english: Or is it just one of 72 fake graves built by the suspicious Cao Cao?
